'''Nimbanese''' was the native [[Language/Legends|language]] of the [[Nimbanel/Legends|Nimbanel]] [[Species/Legends|species]] from [[Nimban/Legends|Nimban]]. Nimbanel snout structure allowed them to articulate different languages, so all were trilingual in Nimbanese, [[Huttese/Legends|Huttese]], and [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].<ref name="Ultimate Alien Anthology" />

